data.description: Seize the opportunity to reside in the heart of Pinellas Park, just 15 minutes from the beaches and 10 minutes for I-275.  This property offers ample space for RV or boat parking, a fenced backyard for entertaining, or even the possibility to install a private pool.  The roof was newly replaced in July 2023, an updated A/C in 2021, and hurricane impact windows installed upstairs.  Enjoy the convenience of tile, LVP, and wood flooring throughout the home, making it easy to maintain for all pet owners.  The spacious laundry area includes built-in cabinets, and the master bedroom in conveniently situated on the first floor.  With no flood insurance required, this home presents a myriad of opportunities for you to make it uniquely yours.
